description:
&lt;p&gt;As the Assistant Director of Finance (Commercial Finance) for one of the largest NHS Foundation Trusts in the country the post holder will, in support of the Director of Finance Strategic Capital and Commerce have responsibility for the delivery of the Trust’s Commercial Finance, Charitable Funds Management and Research, Development and Innovation financial arrangements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be a key member of the Finance team, have the ability to build credibility with, inspire confidence in and demonstrably influence staff at all levels within and outside the organisation. You will contribute to a culture which is patient centred, empowers staff, promotes personal accountability, is fair and collaborative and delivers continuous improvement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NamePaul BradshawJob titleDirector of Finance (Strategic Capital and Commerce)Email addresspaul.bradshaw@liverpoolft.nhs.ukTelephone number01517062000&lt;/p&gt;
